lead_paragraph: Irish fans all over the world celebrated the side's electrifying first-ever victory over the All Blacks, but the historic triumph was tinged with sadness following the recent death at just 42 of former international Anthony "Axel" Foley.

headline.print_headline: Irish Joy Tinged With Sadness as All Blacks Finally Vanquished
